Localization.Name: Second Tevarin War White Dress Jacket
Localization.Description: Carrying Capacity: 1K µSCU\n\nHonor the heroes that served in the Second Tevarin War by wearing a replica Navy uniform. Historically accurate down to every last stitch, period appropriate materials were used to make these uniforms match military specifications of the era. The white Dress Jacket features a sash adorned with metals and was worn for formal occasions and ceremonies.
